{"tid":1528321,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"控制輿論 文宣就位 Twitter戰線就位 連儂牆就位","createTime":"2019-09-01T13:37:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T14:13:30.000Z","uid":34515,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"14e21c47e8d4a3b9edf6afa3cd05ff633b15d464","tid":1528321,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T13:37:10.000Z","msg":"我知 民意並不代表一切<br />\n但民意 係運動升級嘅一個推動力 一個保障<br />\n今日之後 社會上一定會出現更多輿論<br />\n街坊會討論點解要搞東涌站！<br />\n帥奶仔會繼續傾點解要入機場！<br />\n中間派會疑惑關港鐵咩事！<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">我哋嘅目標<br />\n係仲有良心/有人性/想幫我哋呢邊嘅人<span style=\"color: red;\">揾解釋</span></span><br />\n俾個機會佢哋撐我哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無論對方係咩人 我哋都要繼續<span style=\"color: red;\">為前線解釋</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">要同中共鬥 我哋就要控制好輿論<br />\n絕對唔可以因爲宜家有二百萬人就鬆懈</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">煲大黨鐵協助黑警打人同罔顧市民安全<br />\n721白衣人恐怖襲擊<br />\n831黑警無差別打人都係黨鐵發生[red]</span><br />\n文宣嘅作用就係咁！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">解釋！煲大！<br />\n即刻！文宣！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n仲有聽朝電台！打上去！一定要！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">拒絕同温層</span></span><br />\n[red]<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港！<br />\n時代革命！</span></span>"},{"pid":"680a9727023594bc2638982d3bf9e37ae7d0b3e4","tid":1528321,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T13:37:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7b75d7154be017064236a318cd132051c6749f75","tid":1528321,"uid":259345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T13:37:38.000Z","msg":"我地需要你關注<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[推上熱門］［92 &amp; 93］中學生為我地上前線 我地一齊聲援中學生<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1527952\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1527952</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0VUpjiC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0VUpjiC.jpg&h=9cea0167&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dfaa97499aa39fe7253f564d41c3f019f90b5b9b","tid":1528321,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T13:37:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4fbb15943b9dd982b62ee1d12e3cd4c188750dfa","tid":1528321,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T13:37:46.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"8ff2c48d1c796caf09ed92d97a3b8212bcf4f30c","tid":1528321,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T13:38:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"964cbdf045edd83efcc26ec5febd39dbdd5c72c2","tid":1528321,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T13:38:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d76f8bc9a4823fd9bbbc82161e39b6e6185004e5","tid":1528321,"uid":271413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T13:38:14.000Z","msg":"懷疑831太子站有人被失蹤，可能警方失手殺了途人。"},{"pid":"b12c7df000e25683e16fb0357de4a0997cd59d2e","tid":1528321,"uid":191271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T13:38:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">已過5000+正評 現急需最新版中英文宣言 + 文宣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有冇人知點做</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1526412/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1526412/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"bc3d6f0774c017c15a883ec66337783781ad6cbc","tid":1528321,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy